*Stalno* se trudim da naučim nove veštine. (I am constantly trying to learn new skills.)

*Stalno* se nadam da ću postići više. (I am constantly hoping to achieve more.)

*Stalno* se usavršavam. (I am constantly improving myself.)

*Stalno* se trudim da budem bolji. (I am constantly striving to be better.)

*Stalno* se boreći dolazim do cilja. (I am constantly fighting to reach my goal.)

*Stalno* se usmeravam ka uspehu. (I am constantly aiming for success.)